{"word":"Frankincense","slug":"frankincense","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Frankincense</b> An ingredient of the sacred oil<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=34'>Exo 30:34</a><br/> Used with shewbread<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=7'>Lev 24:7</a><br/> Used with meat offerings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=2&verse=2'>Lev 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=2&verse=16'>Lev 2:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=15'>Lev 6:15</a><br/> Prohibited<br/> - In sin offerings when they consist of turtledoves or pigeons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=11'>Lev 5:11</a> <br/> - In making an offering of memorial<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=15'>Num 5:15</a> <br/> A perfume<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=3&verse=6'>Son 3:6</a><br/> Commerce in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=18&verse=13'>Rev 18:13</a><br/> Used as an incense<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=43&verse=23'>Isa 43:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=6'>Isa 60:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=66&verse=3'>Isa 66:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=20'>Jer 6:20</a>"}]}